comment._content:
The US Navy F-14 Tomcat serving as the backdrop (and captured several times in this collection) is BuNo 160395 (c/n 251), a Block 95 Tomcat (F-14A-95-GR).  Today, this Tomcat is on exhibit at the Kalamazoo Aviation History Museum (aka Kalamazoo Air Zoo) in Michigan, on loan from the National Museum of Naval Aviation.  See photo below by dfndr13:
[http://www.flickr.com/photos/11511707@N05/2632321011/]
